{
  "stem": "471.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I tell you the truth.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In some respects, I give him respect.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because when he wrote the book-- when the guy from Australia wrote the book, he call me, beg me that he wants to interview.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He wants to talk to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And believe you me, I couldn't make myself available.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had, at that time, a family.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I couldn't afford to lose-- to lose work.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I had to work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I couldn't-- I couldn't afford to lose the day's work.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I couldn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was [? learning ?] myself.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But anyway-- and people, they're calling the people from the list.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The list is out already.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And people, for money, they're running back and forth.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You know, they're making deals.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It's the same thing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It's not what you know, whom you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So it's-- there were people between ages-- between like, [? and agency, ?] maybe Between them, then they got in to him, to Marcel Goldberg.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He take-- he-- he took the bribery.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I had no money.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I had no money.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, I hear they call my name.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They're loading, already, the people to the boxcar.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They're calling my name.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So I didn't go anymore to the barrack.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I don't know, God must have-- now I come back to God.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe God was over me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they call me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I went-- and that's the way I went into Schindler.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You see?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- How was that for you?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, I tell you the truth, I was already hungry, cold, all broke down.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't think.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I knew, it's-- it's a hope.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If you go to Schindler, it's a hope to survive.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I knew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's a hope only.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "17.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then, 18?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
